## 1. Console-Based Inventory System

**Description:**  
A basic Java console application to manage an inventory of products using `ArrayList`.

**Technologies Used:**  
- Java (JDK 8+)
- Collections (ArrayList)
- Loops, Classes, Scanner

**Features:**  
- Add product with name and quantity  
- Remove product by name  
- List all products

**How to Run:**  
- Compile and run using any IDE or `javac` command.
- No external dependencies required.
